Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:32.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wet myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:37.97,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}Phone Duty - Declare a State of Emergency
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:47.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters Hotline Wiring Maintenance Confirmation for Sudden High-Priority Emergency Contact and Direction Mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:50.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a really long name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:52.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an extremely important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:56.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If we fail, we'll all receive reprimands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:03:01.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the situation, a level-one security alert may be issued,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:05.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and all forces in the area placed on emergency standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:10.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's a heavy responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:13.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh- What kind of mission is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:14.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:18.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Phone duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:27.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how this is the hotline connected to headquarters in the capital, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Has it ever rung?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:30.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:32.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Thankfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So this mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:36.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. It's a good thing that the phone hasn't rung,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:39.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not a good thing if it doesn't ring when necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:44.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So once every six months, they test the line to see if it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:45.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:48.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:50.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, at least remember these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:53.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters Confirmation High-Priority Emergency- Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:58.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's the Headquarters Hotline Wiring Confirmation Emergency for...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:05.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters Hotline Wiring Maintenance Confirmation for Sudden High-Priority Emergency Contact and Direction Mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:11.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Oh! Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:14.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take care of this mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:17.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to try talking on a telephone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:19.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:23.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It works pretty much the same way as the intercom in the Takemicaduchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:25.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that the other side is far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:27.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the amazing part!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:30.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can talk to people so far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:30.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:37.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is a strange feeling to talk to people you can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:40.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But once you get used to it, it's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:44.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The only problem is that we don't know when the call will come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:46.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:47.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:49.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:52.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll be stuck to the phone for the entire day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:05.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Private Kanata Sorami of Platoon 1121 of the Army of the Republic of Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:12.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And when the call is over, we put the phone back the way it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:13.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fil- Fili-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're just so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:04.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? It hurts just to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The train might leave before we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The train?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:11.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have some documents we need to rush to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:14.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus doesn't come until next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're taking them to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:19.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep an eye on that phone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:26.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't answer, they might even think we've been attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep both eyes on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:52.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:54.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:55.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single wink of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Noël around?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:02.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:04.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:06.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The hangar again, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:07.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:10.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So Kanata, what do you want for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I- I- I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:14.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:16.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:23.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Why do you and Kureha never let me cook whenever it's my turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:27.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I cooked all the time before you two got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:31.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn't taste bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:36.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't taste as bad as it looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:37.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:40.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it has a very distinct flavor! It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:41.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:46.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I'll put even more of my love into it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Anyone home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:51.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio, it's Miss Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:57.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:08:01.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I need to stick to the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You've got a customer here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:07.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Guess I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:18.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to eat sandwiches with cutting board in them anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:22.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:25.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and drink. It's apple cider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:29.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's handmade from the farm where we get our apple juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:34.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's like a cousin of the calvados we make?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:34.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:39.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. She found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:41.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.38,0:08:47.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Two should be enough for tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:50.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:51.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:55.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a merchants' guild meeting tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:59.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We always like to provide refreshments as thanks for everything they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:07.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! They did everything they could to hide it from you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:10.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:13.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,W- Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:14.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:17.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get the chance, maybe I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:23.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Miss Naomi, how would you like to have lunch with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:27.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You want me to attend it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:33.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, everyone wants a proper explanation from the military for the news in this week's paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:34.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,News?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:38.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,About how the peace treaty conferences aren't going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:44.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're squabbling over paying reparations and drawing borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:47.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knows these things always take longer than they should.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:53.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more like those old geezers in the guild want to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:57.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since you played the part of one of the Maidens of the Fire at the Water-Casting festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,you've been gaining quite a fanbase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:03.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bother. Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:08.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there. It looks like I'll have to attend the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:12.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of the Maidens of the Fortress now, heart and soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:14.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I will complete this mission by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:17.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. It's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:18.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:24.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, I'd like to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:28.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry they're not new, they were mine before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:31.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't these... trumpet-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:35.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful! Wonderful! Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:40.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your bugling's gotten a lot better recently, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:42.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reward for practicing so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:46.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And with those, you won't fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:54.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is C...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:57.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,D...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,E...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,F...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,G...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:03.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:22.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess summer's just about over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Iliya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:39.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I drank too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:48.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël! Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining! The laundry is getting wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:57.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The courtyard is within the field of operations!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:06.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:08.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:10.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:12.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:14.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:16.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:22.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:27.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:32.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm glad that your laundry is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:35.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So am- I mean-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:38.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you help me after you came all this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:44.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not at all. I'm sorry for the sudden visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:48.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I must return to Treize tomorrow, so I came to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:51.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:53.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though soldiers don't need goodbyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:57.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all, Seiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:13:01.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that Seiya has been disrespectful to you in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:05.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would apologize for that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:07.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the others home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:09.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all out at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:13.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it... Rio? And the black-haired one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:17.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have liked to pay my-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:21.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is this book... yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:22.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a book for the trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:26.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:35.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. I'm sorry. I was just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:38.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:39.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:48.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters Hotline Wiring Maintenance Confirmation for Sudden High-Priority Emergency Contact and Direction Mission
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:49.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:53.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:56.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,you're waiting for this to ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:57.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:14:00.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never used one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:02.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:06.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like whether I can speak properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then would you like to practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:16.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So Sister Yumina is attending the guild meeting too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:22.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she's gone to collect donations from the members of the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:24.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. Drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:28.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:31.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it? Drink up, Seiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:36.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll drink your stupid cider, but don't think I'll like you any more for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:44.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you making?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you two know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:49.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:14:59.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:01.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It is. It's a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:06.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids love them, so sometimes I make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:08.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, Seiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:11.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:16.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:18.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Amazing, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:22.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:25.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, when you pick up a phone, first you say, "Hello."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:27.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you use a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:29.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,H- Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:31.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing! I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can hear his voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:39.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can practice a bit with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:39.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:42.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... This is-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "Hello."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:45.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,H- Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:52.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Private Kanata Sorami of Platoon 1121 of the Army of the Republic of Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:53.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:57.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an honor to receive a call from you at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:00.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, little bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:06.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:08.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio, don't-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:12.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:27.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:49.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me... Are our priest and our-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:11.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:16.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My myriad gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:22.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You only paid a visit to thank them and say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:26.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And instead, you played and made a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:28.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:30.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:31.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:38.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all clean now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:39.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:42.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But your clothes are soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. I have some right over-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:51.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know what we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:17:59.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:01.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, how dazzling you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:08.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sister Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:10.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wash them before I return them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can have them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:15.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're too big for the kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:20.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't imagine anyone who would look so dazzling in them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:25.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you play with us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:29.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back again soon, okay, Seiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I- I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe when I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:44.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:47.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,May the blessings of all be upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:50.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Th- Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:57.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I need to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:00.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:38.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wet myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:30.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:33.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:41.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, those old geezers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:42.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you, Kana-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:46.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio... Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:49.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me... Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:51.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:53.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:57.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wet myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:00.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and do it! You'll get sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:02.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:06.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was holding it in this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:08.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She really does do whatever she's told.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:17.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:20.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:22.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:24.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:27.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:30.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, these people have horrible timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:33.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:38.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Master Sergeant Rio Kazumiya of Platoon 1121 of the Army of the Republic of Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:46.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard we would be confirming your line, so I insisted -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:48.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:49.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:50.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:55.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You simply haven't forgiven me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:59.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After this long. What do you want now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:04.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I want you to save this country! To save Helvetia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:08.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:13.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël, have you been in there since morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:16.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I sleep well in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:18.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.35,0:22:27.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ho- my, Kanata, what cute clothes you're wearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.08,0:22:30.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing in the hallway?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:33.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata fell down. Can't get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:34.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:37.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you just stand up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.77,0:22:43.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:45.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just so spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:47.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.73,0:22:50.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.44,0:22:53.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.57,0:23:03.13,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.49,0:23:06.60,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.78,0:23:24.36,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:30.45,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:39.23,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.46,0:23:43.83,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.86,0:23:45.46,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.55,0:23:49.80,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.88,0:23:51.01,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.01,0:23:56.85,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:54.44,0:23:56.85,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:24:02.82,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.03,0:24:02.82,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:08.82,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.08,0:24:14.66,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.98,0:24:19.61,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.65,0:24:31.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(320,180)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: After a Typhoon - Illusion and Reality.
